OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny overnight mist or fog
OL,6,Faround coasts lifting through the
OL,7,Fmorning but staying dry and rather
OL,8,Fcloudy. Drier and brighter for much of
OL,9,FPerthshire and Western Tayside. A much
OL,10,Fcooler day near coastal areas.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloudy with some drizzle in
OL,13,Fplaces, especially near the coast,
OL,14,Ffeeling cool in light northerly winds.
OL,15,FSome clearer spells developing early
OL,16,Fon Sunday morning.
OL,17,
OL,18,CSunday:FCloudy with the odd shower
OL,19,Fdeveloping in the morning, bright with
OL,20,Fsome sunny spells in the afternoon.
OL,21,FFeeling warm again.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
